text: Boško Marinko (11 August 1939 - 18 July 2020) was a Serbian wrestler. He competed in the 1968 Summer Olympics and 1972 Summer Olympics. Marinko died on 18 July 2020, aged 81. ==References== ==Other websites== * * Category:1939 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Olympians for Yugoslavia Category:Wrestlers
